  "description": [
    "FRIDAY JUNE 221934 Begin Blacklist Terror Against Militant Troflers 9 Fish Buyers Wont Take Members By A Fisherman Westport WashAt the Instiga tion of the social fascist leader Mr John Suoja and his henchmen of the Pacific Coast Fisheries Union a blacklist system has been started against all militant trollers mem hers of the Fishermen and Cannery Workers Industrial Union Recentlv a meeting was called hv Mr Kalle Maki and Mr Lanto delegates of Mr Suoia to put throngh a motion forcing all the members of the FCWILT into des troving their wnian emblem from their boats This motion was re jected by the rank and file but when the meeting was nearly over and the majority of fishermen had left the meeting Suojas henchmen snueceeded In putting thtrough this vicions motion with the aid of a handful of renegades from the waorking class movement Fish Buyers Aid Fascists Makl and Lanto first and second lieutenant respectively of Suoja are now spending most of their time instead of trolling lintimidat ing the local fish buvers prevent ing them from accepting fish from the members of the FCWIU Karl and Backman buvers for the San Junan Packing Company last week carried"
